title: TI 84 Plus CE graphing calculator
description:
Introducing TI’s next-generation graphing calculator. It delivers  familiar TI-84 Plus functionality in a sleek new design that features a crisp color screen.
Surprisingly slimmer. Lots lighter. Totally TI-84 Plus.
Learn more at: http://www.education.ti.com/84ce
